title: The Ace Family vs Shyla Waller… the sequel
description:
This week on Fool Coverage we have rapid fire! Manny and Laura cover Andrew Tate getting removed from all social media, The Ace Family vs Shyla Waller...the sequeal, Kim Kardashian's Paris abductor getting an interview with the press, House of the Dragon breaking the HBO Max App, and more! Rapid fire starts at 26:00 in case yall are wondering haha.
